{
  "text": "Patients randomized to citalopram were prescribed 20 mg daily. Citalopram taken at this dose has been shown to occupy about 80% of serotonin transporter reuptake sites, which is reported to be the level of occupancy needed to produce reliable antidepressant effects [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
